<br>
Hmmmm, Verant really does not understand the Bard class.  Give us a FA weapon?  Ha!  Here's my wish for what they gave us instead.<br>
<br>
Momma's Little Squeeze Box<br>
Instrument Lore No Drop<br>
Wt. 7.0<br>
Effect: String/Wind/Brass/Drum<br>
+45% to all song effects<br>
<br>
That's right.  I want a sqeeze box!  Let bards be bards, not warrior want-to-be's.  Just imagine, song battling without switching instruments.  Yes, the drum effect would be weak, just imagine thumping the side or something.  I'd also hate to think of the graphic and animation they'd put in for it.  But this would be cool.  Yes, they are heavy too.  I could also see your stamina drop while singing.<br>
<br>
But no, we get a small blade with dripping notes.  Maybe we'll get lucky and the effect on the blade will be an instrument skill and not some spell.<br>
<br>
Anyway, just some thoughts over the weekend. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
